# Food-photo AI analysis (Google Gemini, free tier).
# Without this, the app uses a built-in demo estimator so the feature still works.
#
# To enable real analysis:
#   1. Go to https://aistudio.google.com/apikey  and create a free API key
#   2. Copy this file to ".env.local" and paste your key below
#   3. Restart the dev server
#
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your-key-here
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash
